Implemented the controller in:

- `components/controller/controller.c`

Behavior added:

- boot defaults to pump off
- low level `< 30` turns pump on
- high level `> 80` turns pump off
- mid-band `30..80` holds previous pump output and reports `HOLDING`
- malformed input forces safe off
- explicit timeout input forces safe off
- idle/no-new-frame only times out after `> 1000 ms`; otherwise preserves prior output

